My biggest fashion inspiration is gone. Can’t quite put my feelings into words. Dear Karl, you made a little girl from Queens want to be glamorous. I prayed I’d get to work with you b4 one of us left this earth, thank you for making my dreams come true. When everyone on set was afraid you’d think my hair was too long, you pulled me to the side & said “brilliant!!!” 😢 Thank you. You are the best to ever do it. Genius. Icon. Game changer. Can’t imagine the fashion world w/o you. Rest In Peace. Legends never die. #ChanelForever #FendiPrintsOnForever. ♥️🙏🏽
